375
00:17:32,872 --> 00:17:34,272
Doh-doh.

376
00:17:34,272 --> 00:17:36,472
I finally figured out that

377
00:17:36,472 --> 00:17:40,272
the belt of the bag was frozen only after dad dropped me a hint.

378
00:17:40,272 --> 00:17:42,072
That's why as far as the intermediate school boy

379
00:17:42,072 --> 00:17:43,672
that solved this case alone,

380
00:17:43,672 --> 00:17:45,672
I don't want to see him.

381
00:17:45,672 --> 00:17:46,972
Why not?

382
00:17:46,972 --> 00:17:48,472
Why should I go when you're the one who solved the case?

383
00:17:48,472 --> 00:17:50,472
Take the PET bottle along with you,

384
00:17:50,472 --> 00:17:54,472
and tell him that you solved the case by yourself.

385
00:17:54,472 --> 00:17:55,772
I only figured everything out

386
00:17:55,772 --> 00:17:57,572
after dad told me the story of the Snow Woman

387
00:17:57,572 --> 00:18:00,872
who pretended that she sprained her leg and went into the basket.

388
00:18:00,872 --> 00:18:03,772
That's when I figured out that Mr. Minowa who wanted to pretend

389
00:18:03,772 --> 00:18:06,672
that he was a good skier went into the bag himself.

390
00:18:06,672 --> 00:18:09,272
But your deduction was correct, wasn't it?

391
00:18:09,272 --> 00:18:12,272
No, this case was solved by the intermediate school boy

392
00:18:12,272 --> 00:18:14,972
who figured everything out himself, not me.

393
00:18:14,972 --> 00:18:17,072
-Hey. -Quiet.

394
00:18:17,072 --> 00:18:18,472
That's what you get for coming along with me,

395
00:18:18,472 --> 00:18:19,772
despite having sprained your leg!

396
00:18:19,772 --> 00:18:22,272
I'll bet you sprained your leg when practicing

397
00:18:22,272 --> 00:18:25,172
just so you could brag that you're an advanced skier.

398
00:18:25,172 --> 00:18:26,972
Well, thanks to you showing off,

399
00:18:26,972 --> 00:18:30,472
I figured out why Mr. Minowa went into the bag right away,

400
00:18:30,472 --> 00:18:32,472
and you also helped with a lot of things

401
00:18:32,472 --> 00:18:34,172
so I guess I'll forgive you.

402
00:18:34,172 --> 00:18:37,072
Idiot. I didn't practice

403
00:18:37,072 --> 00:18:39,972
because I wanted to show everybody how good I was.

404
00:18:41,272 --> 00:18:45,472
I wonder why there are two different stories about the Snow Woman?

405
00:18:45,472 --> 00:18:49,472
I'll bet it's because the storyteller was a mother.

406
00:18:49,472 --> 00:18:51,172
It's said that the folk tale of Snow Woman

407
00:18:51,172 --> 00:18:55,072
