413
00:19:09,572 --> 00:19:12,772
but it changed to a story in which, she did not take the soul,

414
00:19:12,772 --> 00:19:14,572
but rather, just melted into snow.

415
00:19:14,572 --> 00:19:16,572
That's why the stories of Snow Woman

416
00:19:16,572 --> 00:19:19,372
