417
00:19:26,972 --> 00:19:29,272
I couldn't see very well because of the snow.

418
00:19:29,272 --> 00:19:32,072
But I'll bet it's him that intermediate school boy.

419
00:19:32,072 --> 00:19:35,072
Well, even if I don't see him, if he's a detective...

